    "Management": {
      "text": "Treatment (to reduce rheumatic fever / nephritis)\nPenicillin VK\n50mg/kg BID x 10d\nOR\nAmoxicillin\n50mg/kg/d in 2 divided doses or one time dose x10d\n[1]\nIf allergic to penicillin →\nAzithromycin\n10mg/kg on day 1, 5mg/g days 2-5",
